<i>A rare and unique</i>
<i>Chinese weapon,</i>

30:42.132 --> 30:44.634
<i>the wind and fire wheels</i>
<i>were multi-functional tools</i>

30:44.634 --> 30:48.472
<i>utilized in martial arts</i>
<i>dating back over 500 years.</i>

30:48.472 --> 30:50.640
<i>Approximately one foot</i>
<i>in diameter,</i>

30:50.640 --> 30:53.143
<i>the wheels featured</i>
<i>a sturdy-wrapped grip,</i>

30:53.143 --> 30:55.854
<i>along with short, but lethal,</i>
<i>protruding blades.</i>

30:55.854 --> 30:57.731
<i>Those trained</i>
<i>in the use of the weapon</i>

