35:58.073 --> 35:59.741
- Morning on day five.

35:59.741 --> 36:02.994
Today I have grinding.
A little bit of grinding.

36:02.994 --> 36:05.246
<i>I might throw in</i>
<i>some more grinding.</i>

36:05.246 --> 36:08.083
I think my biggest concern
with these heading into testing

36:08.083 --> 36:10.085
<i>is one of my welds failing.</i>

36:10.085 --> 36:12.379
That's really the weak point
of these.

36:12.379 --> 36:15.382
<i>[upbeat music]</i>

36:15.382 --> 36:17.384
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:17.384 --> 36:19.552
It will kill.

36:19.552 --> 36:26.351
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:28.103 --> 36:29.145
Mm.

36:30.438 --> 36:33.608
<i>[tense music]</i>

36:33.608 --> 36:35.443
<i>♪ ♪</i>

36:35.443 --> 36:39.155
- Rebel, Chuck,
welcome back to The Forge.

36:39.155 --> 36:41.241
